{{Quote|It's not that I don't appreciate the beauty of the Agrilat Swamp. Boiling showers and razor-sharp grass are a joy to experience. But when the swamp's larger wildlife chooses to wander into more civilized areas, I've got to draw the line. The farmers in the area are getting worried.|Moss Shelby|<ref name="SWG:LCotM">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=terminal||Large Creatures on the Move}} on Corellia</ref>}}
'''Moss Shelby''' was an [[Officer/Legends|officer]] of the [[Corellian Security Force]] who lived on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. After the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], he was a [[Lieutenant/Legends|lieutenant]] in CorSec [[Regiment Twelve]].<ref name="SWG:LCotM" /> When, in [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]],<ref name="SWG_timeline">{{SWG_timeline}}</ref> large creatures from the [[Agrilat Region|Agrilat Swamp]] wandered into more civilized areas of Corellia and local farmers began to get worried, they asked Shelby for help. As Shelby did not want to waste CorSec resources on this, the lieutenant hired a group of [[Spacer/Legends|spacers]] to do the job.<ref name="SWG:LCotM" />

==Behind the scenes==
Moss Shelby was mentioned in the [[2003]] [[Star Wars video games|video game]] [[Star Wars Galaxies|''Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided'']], a [[Roleplaying game|massively multiplayer online role-playing game]] developed by [[Sony]] Online Entertainment and published by [[LucasArts]],<ref name="SWG:LCotM" /> prior to its closure on [[December 15]], [[2011]].<ref name="Shutdown">{{SonyCite|url=playerinfo|text=IMPORTANT INFORMATION ABOUT ''STAR WARS'' GALAXIES™}}</ref> Shelby was mentioned in a mission called "Large Creatures on the Move" available on [[mission terminal]]s on Corellia.<ref name="SWG:LCotM" />

